      <div n="urn:cts:cdli:P346683.P346683.cdli-sux" type="edition" xml:lang="sux">
        <div n="tablet" type="textpart">
          <div n="obverse" type="textpart">
            <l n="1'">[...]-⸢ga⸣ ⸢šu⸣ [...]-x-[...]</l>
            <l n="2'">[...] ki-x-am3 ša3-ga ⸢nu⸣-da13-da13#!</l>
            <l n="3'">[...] ⸢nig2⸣-gur11-ra HAR-HAR la-ba-gu7!?</l>
            <l n="4'">[...] i7-da ma2 he2-da-BAD</l>
            <l n="5'">[...]-⸢na⸣ {kuš}ummu3 he2-em-dar-dar</l>
            <l n="6'">[...] ⸢ag2⸣ nig2 e2 du3-du3-e</l>
            <l n="7'">[...] nig2#!? e2 gul-gul-e</l>
          </div>
          <div n="reverse" type="textpart">
            <l n="1">[...]-⸢du8⸣-du8 gaba-gal2 me nam-nun-na-ra#?</l>
            <l n="2">[...] ⸢gu2⸣ he2-bi2-ni-gar?</l>
            <l n="3">[...] ⸢ni2⸣-zu he2-ni-ne-la2</l>
            <l n="4">[...] ⸢hul⸣-ur2 he2-en-ši-gal2</l>
            <l n="5">[...]-⸢ka⸣ dam na-ba-du12-du12</l>
            <l n="6">[...] ⸢bar⸣-ra hun!-ga2-am3</l>
            <l n="7">[...] x x x hun-ga2-am3</l>
            <l n="8">[...] ⸢za⸣-gin3 hun!-ga2-am3</l>
            <l n="9">[...] x mu-un-da-sa2-a</l>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div type="translation">
        <div n="tablet" type="textpart"/>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
        <l n="1'">Evil does not forget the heart (either)</l>
        <l n="2'">Goodness is a fertile spot, it cannot be abandoned in the heart</l>
        <l n="3'">Evil consumes property (like) fodder/debt(?)</l>
        <l n="4'">May the boat be far away from/block/die along with(?) the evildoer in the river(?)</l>
        <l n="5'">The waterskin should split apart in the desert</l>
        <l n="6'">A loving heart is something that builds a house</l>
        <l n="7'">A hating heart is something that destroys a house</l>
        <l n="1">To the authoritative one, possessor of riches, forcefulness(?), and the “rites” of princeliness</l>
        <l n="2">One should submit to the authoritative</l>
        <l n="3">You should attach yourself to(?) the powerful</l>
        <l n="4">My son, one should be against(?) the evildoer</l>
        <l n="5">One should not marry in “that of a festival”</l>
        <l n="6">Inside ... is rented, outside ... is rented</l>
        <l n="7">The ... is rented, the ... is rented</l>
        <l n="8">The silver is rented, the lapis is rented</l>
        <l n="9">... is one that(?) compares with ...</l>
      </div>
